                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>\n                <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear Sir!</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Enclosed I forward<lb/> you by friend <persName>G. Kursheedt\n                    Esq.</persName> the balance of our account<lb/> say Thirty Seven Dollars. I hope\n                you will pardon me<lb/> for my neglect in not sending it before, but rest\n                assured<lb/> that <sic>unforseen</sic> circumstances, which <persName>Mr\n                    K</persName> can explain to you<lb/> were the cause. Hoping this will meet you\n                in the best<lb/> enjoyment of health. I remain</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">Respectfully yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">B. da Silva</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p><placeName>New Orleans</placeName>\n                <date>May 25<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1854</date>.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3sx64w3g/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
